headline: Is Expeditors International Still Attractive After 26% Rally and New Logistics Contracts in 2025?
summary: Wondering if Expeditors International of Washington is priced for opportunity or risk? You are not alone. Valuation is often top-of-mind for investors right now. The stock’s performance has been eye-catching. After gaining 15.5% over the past month, it is up an impressive 26.5% year-to-date and 18.5% over the last year.
